/* ==========================================
   VINCE TALK TOPICS — COMMON PHASE, LEVEL 1
   phase === "common" && friendshipLevel === 1

   CHARACTER: Vince Rossi, Manager at Ruby's Diner
   → Performative businessman, always selling something.
   → Distant but subtly creepy/uncomfortable. Never says it out loud.
   → Physical closeness and lingering looks replace actual words.

   COMMON L1 TONE:
   → Player has no job, just dropped by.
   → Vince plays the friendly manager.

   CONTEXTS:
   dinerRubys_common_morning
   dinerRubys_common_afternoon
   dinerRubys_common_evening
========================================== */

