text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/vince/level1/vinceCommonMorning-1.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Vince steps out from behind the counter, standing just a bit too close as you wait.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>Morning, morning. Nice of you to visit us today. We love seeing friendly faces early in the day.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Morning, Vince.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>_(smiles, eyes dropping to your collar for a millisecond)_ Always looking sharp. Stay as long as you like. Coffee's fresh.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>I'll get some soon.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>Take your time. I'll be watching the floor.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 1, trust: 0
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/vince/level1/vinceCommonMorning-2.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Vince is straightening menus, making sure the logo faces perfectly forward.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>A well-run diner is a piece of art. People don't realize the details that go into it. Do you?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Usually I just look at the food.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>Most people do. But the ones paying attention... they see everything.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>I guess so.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>_(pats the counter)_ Enjoy your morning.<</dialog>`,
