            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/vince/level1/vinceCommonMorning-3.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Vince blocks the aisle slightly as he adjusts his tie.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>Beautiful morning out there, isn't it? Makes me wish I wasn't trapped handling logistics all day.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>You're the boss.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>A heavy crown. But seeing bright young people like you walk through my doors makes it easier. Truly.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Uh, okay. Sure.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>Don't mention it. Let me know if the girls treat you right.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 0
