<<dialog "dinerManager">>Emma does a good job. A little messy around the edges, but she listens.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>She works hard.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>Hard work is exactly what I pay for. Nothing more, nothing less.
_(looks at you slowly)_
You look like a hard worker.<</dialog>>
