<<dialog "player">>Three minutes isn't that bad.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>It's a reflection of respect. I tolerate it because I'm a forgiving man. Most men aren't as forgiving.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>If you say so, Vince.<</dialog>>
