<<dialog "dinerManager">>Managing people is like herding cats. You have to know exactly what motivates them.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Usually money.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>_(laughs quietly)_ Money is easy. It's the other things that make people truly loyal. I'm working on that.<</dialog>>
